libbeagle: libbeagle (Beagle Indexing and Searching Library)
libbeagle:
libbeagle: libbeagle is a standalone C library interface to the Beagle desktop
libbeagle: search and indexing system.  Users of libbeagle can search the Beagle
libbeagle: indexes as well as send data to the service to be indexed.  Although
libbeagle: the Beagle daemon is written using C# and Mono, there is no Mono
libbeagle: dependency when using this library.
